      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_shi_zhe",
      "text": "你要我替你做事，当然要先放我走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_shi_zhe",
      "text": "你相信我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我相信。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_shi_zhe",
      "text": "你认为我是个随时都会出卖朋友的人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我知道你不是，但他们并不是你的朋友，老皮却是的，还有小琳。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "所以只要你答应我，我立刻放你走，在十五日出之前，你若不带他们来，那么你的小琳就……",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_shi_zhe",
      "text": "我只一有点儿想不通。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你可以问。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_shi_zhe",
      "text": "你们最恨的本来是我。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_shi_zhe",
      "text": "轿子里那个人，却只不过是个陌生的过路客，而且还有重病。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_shi_zhe",
      "text": "现在你们宁可为了他而放过我，他对你为什么如此重要？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "他值钱。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_shi_zhe",
      "text": "值多少钱？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "多得你连做梦都想不到。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你应该感激我，我没有让你吃草，可是我已经给你吃了另一种药！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_shi_zhe",
      "text": "什么药？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "当然是毒药。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
