      "speaker_name": "使者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "十五的日出之前，你若还没有把人带来，你就会知道那是种什么样的毒药了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "人呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "我那些朋友。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "那些人已经走了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "什么时候走的？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "当然是算过账才走的，已经走了很久，他们急着赶路。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你不想去追他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "你知道他们走的哪条路？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我只知道无论他们走的是哪条路，都是条死路，所以你就算追上他们也没有用。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我说的是老实话。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我知道你一定又遇上了麻烦，而且麻烦一定不小。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我们总算也是朋友，我也很想帮帮你的忙，只可惜这里是狼山，无论谁在这里遇上了麻烦，都绝对没有人能替他解决的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "也许还有一个人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "狼山之王。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "只要有朱五太爷的一句话，当然什么问题都可以解决了，只可惜……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "只可惜我找不到他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "非但你找不到，简直就没有人能找得到他。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "我知道一定有个人的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "你！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "不是我，真的不是……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "你带我去，我绝不会害你，朱五也绝不会怪你，因为我只不过是送礼去的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "送礼？送什么礼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "送我的这双拳头！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "否则我就将这双拳头送给你！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你就算打死我，我也没法子带你去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "我并不想打死你，死人不会带路，没有鼻子的人却一样可以带路。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "没有鼻子的人也一样找不到他老人家！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "如果连眼珠子也少掉一个呢？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "那……那……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "也许那也没有什么了不起，可是男人身上，有样东西是万万不能少的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "现在你是不是已经想起他在哪里了？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "有一点儿，好像有一点儿，你总得让我慢慢的想。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "你要想多久？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jin_lian",
      "speaker_name": "柳金莲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你就算让他再想三年，他也想不起来的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jin_lian",
      "speaker_name": "柳金莲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你想找朱五太爷，只有一个人可以带你去找。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_liu_jin_lian",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jin_lian",
      "speaker_name": "柳金莲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_liu_jin_lian",
      "text": "你肯带我去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jin_lian",
      "speaker_name": "柳金莲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "只要你答应我一件事。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_liu_jin_lian",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jin_lian",
      "speaker_name": "柳金莲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你们杀了章长脚，你总得赔个老公给我。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_liu_jin_lian",
      "text": "这个人不但会说话，而且会赚钱，做老公正是再好也没有的了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我不行，我是个……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_liu_jin_lian",
      "text": "我就把他赔给你做老公，你看好不好？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jin_lian",
      "speaker_name": "柳金莲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "不好。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_liu_jin_lian",
      "text": "你想要个什么样的男人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_jin_lian",
      "speaker_name": "柳金莲",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我要的就是你！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "是我。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "原来是你！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "就是我。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你知道我平生最倒霉的事是什么？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "是认得那个老太婆？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "只不过我平生最走运的事，也是认得了她。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "若不是她，现在我已经只能到十八层地狱里去做生意。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "所以你一定要报她的恩？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "所以你现在还活着。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "现在我们走的是什么路？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "那就得看你了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "看我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你若走得对，这就是狼山上唯一的一条活路。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "我若走得不对？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "那么你跟我就要被打下十八层地狱，万劫不复。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "除了阎王之外，还有谁能把我们打下十八层地狱？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "还有一个王。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "text": "还有一个什么王？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hao_sheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "郝生意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "狼王之王。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    }
